==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Outslide
<hw>Out*slide"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To slide
outward, onward, or forward; to advance by sliding.</def>
<mark>[Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>At last our grating keels <qex>outslide</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Whittier.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Outsoar</ent>⟦br⟧
